{"tid":1286103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非最大嘅誤會係03年推倒23條","createTime":"2019-07-04T18:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T20:29:00.000Z","uid":111253,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"569acf5170de2200d2c5a4775a0a357d3505b9a8","tid":1286103,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:54:32.000Z","msg":"點解當年50萬人上街成功，<br />\n今次成百萬人都冇成果？<br />\n<br />\n因為經濟崩潰，當年沙士經濟幾低迷唔洗講，自98年港爆咗唔夠5年就整獲沙士你嘆，啲人遊行主要係搵唔到食，反23條係順勢<br />\n<br />\n加上當時支那對港政策仲未咁強勢，冇而家習總咁撚癲，時任特首董伯伯又係個廢鳩嚟嘅，所以先會退<br />\n<br />\n睇返今日經濟環境，黨主席係乜水，就知道港共係唔撚會理你幾多人上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9488b7c14eff79ab5659850a0cd3fe77e83cad6","tid":1286103,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1f06c24270624e76e2e5d09f1d7d42cf77ff107","tid":1286103,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:56:17.000Z","msg":"雖然最後都係鳩行 靠12號先阻到<br />\n但9/6前本土派好似你咁諗 最後其實炒哂車<br />\n今日大家有工開有飯食都出黎行係覺醒左"},{"pid":"7b16e116c1b0e6b0ad91fcfdaba94c2467b47a9a","tid":1286103,"uid":203889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:56:46.000Z","msg":"果時好似係因為田少<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>1.我無野講 2.我要見律師<br />\n3.！！絕不解鎖！！(唔記得左密碼//就算解都要有律師在場）<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察 被捕須知懶人包：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XLSCy9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XLSCy9&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=e7fd03ed\" data